import React, {useState} from 'react';
import { View, TextInput, ScrollView, Text, ImageBackground, TouchableOpacity, Image } from 'react-native';
import styles from './style';

import She from '../../assets/she.png'
import Fundo from '../../assets/fundo.png';
import { Icon } from 'react-native-vector-icons/Icon';


function Perfil({navigation}) {
   
  return (
    <ScrollView style={styles.fundoContainer}>   
    
      <View  style={styles.caixaPerfil}>
        <Text style={styles.titulo}>Perfil</Text>
      
        <View style={styles.imgBox}>
          <Image source={She} style={styles.she}/>
          <Text style={styles.nomeJogador}>Anna</Text>
        </View>

        <View>       
          <Text>Nível</Text>
          <Text>2</Text>
        </View>
        <View>
          <Text>Medalhas Conquistadas</Text>
          <Text>8</Text>
        </View>
        <View>
          <Text>Colocação no Ranking</Text>
          <Text>5°</Text>
        </View>
        <View>
          <TextInput />
        </View>
        <View>
          <Icon />
        </View>
      
      

        


      </View>
      
    </ScrollView>
  )
  
}

export default Perfil;
